				<font face="verdana" size="3"><a name="19">Bertoxx Event - 3v3 Teams Tourney - Saints of Blood and Honor</a></font><br>
				<font face="verdana" size="2">
				<b><a href="mailto:Shroomer2@aol.com">Gravesion Gravedigger</b></a>
				[7/16/2001-2:16:37 PM]</font>
				&nbsp;<a href="Comments.asp?ID=467734"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Comments[0]</font></a><p>
				<font face="verdana" size="2"><blockquote>
<p>
Greetings Norrathians!</p>
<p>
I am pleased to inform you that the Saints of Blood and Honor is hosting a 3v3 tournament, on Wednesday, July 18, at 8pm EDT (5pm PDT) in The Arena.</p>
<p>
Each team is made up of 3 members, all of which must fit into the same level bracket. The brackets are:</p>
<p>
10-15<br>
15-20<br>
20-30<br>
30-45<br>
45+</p>
<p>
Entry fee is 2pp per person, per level. When your team is called up to fight, you will have 30 seconds to buff yourself and your teammates, summon any pets, and equip yourself as necessary. The fight will go until all of the members of one team die, and the other team is pronounced as the winners.</p>
<p>
Officers of the Saints of Blood and Honor are serving as the judges, and will also be providing alcohol =)</p>
<p>
The fighting is pretty much No Holds Barred, any form of Charm, Fear, Item Effects, and other Cheap Fighting Tactics are not only allowed but encouraged. The only rules are no fighting before the fight command is given, and no interference from spectators.</p>
<p>
The winner in each level bracket will collect all the money from that level backet, to be evenly divided up amongst the team members.</p>
<p>
If you wish to enter this event, please E-mail <A HREF="" >Shroomer2@aol.com</a> and include the names, levels, and classes of you and your teammates, and I will get back to you regarding registration.</p>
<p>
Gravesion Gravedigger<br>
Leader of Saints of Blood and Honor</p>
</blockquote></font></p><p>&nbsp;</p>
		
