<p>
When: Sunday, July 15, 2001. NOON EST<br>
Where: Race begins in the Lake of Ill Omen. Just outside cabilis gates.<br>
Description: Racers will chug down as much mead as their puny bodies can take, and then race to the lake. They will then swim across (meeting checkpoints along the way) to the other side where they will run up into the Sarnak fort and onto the platform. Contestants will chug another stack of mead and run inside the fort. First person to /poke Chancellor Di'Zok wins the race. If the Chancellor is dead, first person to sit in his chair.</p>
<p>
Cost:<br>
5pp for lvl 10-20<br>
15pp for lvl 21-30<br>
25pp for lvl 31-40<br>
35pp for lvl 41-50<br>
50pp for lvl 51+</p>
<p>
50% of the pot will go to first place winner, 20% will go to second place winner. The rest will be distributed to those members of the Royalty of Norrath who help.</p>
<p>
Again, the Drunken Chancellor Tap will be held on Karana, Sunday July 15, at Noon EST. E-mail <a href="mailto:Mylkathros@aol.com">Mylkathros@aol.com</a> with your characters name and level if you will be there. Also you may contact me in-game by giving a tell to Nysil.   Racers, good luck.</p>
<p>
-Nysil<br>
-29th monk of Cazic-Thule<br>
-Hail Karana Server</p>
